      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a dream to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super clean inside and out, and it runs like a champ! I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019m looking for someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Perfect for daily commutes or weekend road trips. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
