    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable example of pride in ownership, offering a seamless blend of performance and reliability. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, showing only the lightest evidence of careful road use. Inside, the cabin feels like a sanctuary; the premium upholstery is soft and well-preserved, and all technological features\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system\u2014operate exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine is responsive and quiet, benefited by a strict adherence to every scheduled maintenance interval. We recently completed a full multi-point inspection, fresh oil service, and confirmed the brake pads and tires have significant life remaining. This car drives straight, shifts smoothly, and is ready to provide its next owner with years of dependable, stylish transportation.",
      "price": 36500.0,
