    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my reliable daily driver and it's looking for a brand new adventure. It\u2019s been such a fantastic car for me\u2014super dependable and still looks and drives great! I've made sure to keep up with it so it's ready to hit the road the moment you take the keys. If you're looking for a solid, well-cared-for ride that won't let you down, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to tell you more about it!",
