    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double VANOS system. The powerplant delivers a linear torque curve and a visceral 8,000 RPM redline, channeled through a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip differential. The chassis integrity is preserved with reinforced subframe mounting points and a refreshed suspension geometry. Recent service includes a comprehensive valve adjustment and rod bearing inspection, ensuring the internal reciprocating assembly is within factory tolerances. While showing honest signs of road use, this machine remains mechanically sharp and ready for the circuit or spirited canyon runs.",
